  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_OFFER_CURE",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      {
        "math": [ "human_blood_vitamin > 0" ],
        "yes": "Before that, you must starve yourself of blood so I know you genuinely want to be freed.  Return to me when you will show symptoms of blood starvation and I will cure you.",
        "no": "You starved yourself of blood.  Good.  Now lie there on the dirt and stay perfectly still while the heartvines do their work.  It'll take half an hour, it'll hurt and you'll probably need a few days to recover, but you won't become another victim of this curse."
      }
    ],
    "responses": [
      {
        "text": "Go ahead.",
        "topic": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_PERFORM_CURE",
        "condition": {
          "and": [
            { "math": [ "human_blood_vitamin < 1" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('head') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('torso') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('arm_l') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('arm_r') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('leg_l') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
            { "math": [ "u_hp('leg_r') >= u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "effect": [
          { "u_assign_activity": "ACT_GENERIC_EOC", "duration": "30 minutes" },
          { "run_eocs": "EOC_BLOODTHORNE_DRUID_PURGE_VAMPIRISM_IN_OTHER", "alpha_talker": "avatar" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "Go ahead.",
        "topic": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_CURE_WARNING",
        "condition": {
          "and": [
            { "math": [ "human_blood_vitamin < 1" ] },
            {
              "or": [
                { "math": [ "u_hp('head') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
                { "math": [ "u_hp('torso') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
                { "math": [ "u_hp('arm_l') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
                { "math": [ "u_hp('arm_r') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
                { "math": [ "u_hp('leg_l') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] },
                { "math": [ "u_hp('leg_r') < u_vampire_bloodthorne_maximal_cure_damage()" ] }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_CURE_WARNING",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "I must warn you before we start.  Your fragilized body and your potent vampirism mean that the heartvines will cause severe damage to your body.  You could die from the procedure.  Are you sure you want to do this?"
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "I will find another way", "topic": "TALK_DONE" },
      {
        "text": "Do it.  <color_red>This might literally kill you.</color>",
        "topic": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_PERFORM_CURE",
        "effect": [
          { "u_assign_activity": "ACT_GENERIC_EOC", "duration": "30 minutes" },
          { "run_eocs": "EOC_BLOODTHORNE_DRUID_PURGE_VAMPIRISM_IN_OTHER", "alpha_talker": "avatar" }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_PERFORM_CURE",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "And done.  You're now free from vampirism for the time being.  Take some time to recover, and ask Blaine if you ever want to buy a less painful cure from him."
    ],
    "responses": [ { "text": "thanks.  <end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" } ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_INTRO",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "I can use my heartvines to cure people from vampirism.  I let the heartvines enter their veins where the curse will be destroyed by the heartvines and their intense desire to kill all vampires.  It's painful for them, but it's better than staying a vampire."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "What's a heartvine?", "topic": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_INNER_PLANT" },
      { "text": "Cool.  <end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_BLOODTHORNE_INNER_PLANT",
    "//": "Maybe she'll offer the player to become a Bloodthorne druid someday, but not for now.",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "That's how Bloodthorne druids call the plant inside them.  It empowers us through the essence of nature spirits so we may kill the blood-drinkers.  Before you ask, I can't help you become one.  I wasn't taught how to do this before I lost contact with other Bloodthorne druids."
    ],
    "responses": [ { "text": "<end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" } ]
